@startuml
title Quarto rendering pipeline

actor Author
participant "QMD source" as QMD
participant "Quarto CLI" as Quarto
participant "Reveal.js" as Reveal
participant "TinyTeX" as TeX

Author -> QMD: write content
Author -> Quarto: quarto render
Quarto -> Reveal: render HTML slides
Quarto -> TeX: render PDF
Reveal --> Author: .html
TeX --> Author: .pdf
@enduml
